##  Technologies Used

- **HTML5** (semantic and accessible)
- **CSS3** (no frameworks)
- **JavaScript** (vanilla ES6, no libraries)
- **GitHub Version Control**

---

##  Development Notes

This project was developed iteratively in GitHub to demonstrate:
- consistent version control
- meaningful commit messages
- accessibility improvements over time
- real testing feedback applied into code updates

Example commit timeline:
- setup basic structure  
- add form + styling  
- improve accessibility  
- run WAVE test â†’ fix errors  
- add aria-live + keyboard refinements  
- final tidy up  

